Date: Fri, 14 Mar 2025 14:25:05 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add bmc reboot event log # Description: - Modify the function
 "lastRebootCause" to not only log the message in   journal but also record it
 in the event log after a BMC reboot.

# Motivation:
- Since the BMC currently does not have a reboot event log, adding this
  feature will help with debugging when issues occur.

# Test Plan:
- Reset the BMC and check the event log - pass

# Test result:
- WatchdogReset
